---
const title = "Carol Lab";
---

<section class="welcome">
  <h1>{title}</h1>
  <p>這裡是我的個人作品與設計分享空間。專注於 Logo 與字體設計，希望你會喜歡我的作品！</p>
</section>

<style>
  .welcome {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
    color: #ffffffcc;
    max-width: 1024px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .welcome h1 {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    margin: 0;
    flex: 1;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .welcome p {
    flex: 1;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: left;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .welcome {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .welcome h1,
    .welcome p {
      text-align: center;
      flex: unset;
    }
  }
</style>

